# World-content closeout checklist

Use this checklist when closing or re-scoping `#60`, `#69`, `#62`, `#63`, or `#64`.

## Required references
- Parent epic or child issue reference
- Prerequisite contracts issue for `mapLocationId -> dagLocationSlot`
- Local artifact bundle path under `artifacts/qa-runs/functional-qa/world-content/<lane-or-issue>/<timestamp>/`

## Proof expectations
- Validation summary for current behavior
- Explicit blocker or close-ready status
- Verification command transcript
- Reviewer-visible proof links for any UI-visible acceptance artifact
- Pack, manifest, or reward diff summary as applicable

## Closeout checklist
- [ ] Confirm the prerequisite contracts issue exists and is referenced.
- [ ] Confirm the issue body or comment names the current live map pins or slot targets it depends on.
- [ ] Record the local artifact bundle path.
- [ ] Run the prerequisite regression command set and save output under `verification/`.
- [ ] Post a GitHub issue update with artifact path, verification result, and closeout status.
- [ ] If close-ready, add PR-ready notes with title, summary, `Fixes`/`Refs`, and `How to test`.
